sequenceDiagram
    participant Win as Windows
    participant Pump as Event pump
    participant Lock as Lock coordinator
    participant Cmd as Authorized command
    participant Mem as Sensitive state
    participant Ev as Evidence sink
    Lock->>Mem: initialize locked
    Lock->>Ev: state_changed(locked, epoch 0)
    Note over Lock,Mem: Unlock de prova instala apenas canário controlado
    Cmd->>Lock: begin_authorized()
    Lock-->>Cmd: guard(epoch 7)
    Win->>Pump: WTS lock ou pre-suspend
    Pump->>Lock: lock(system_event)
    activate Lock
    Lock->>Lock: increment epoch
    Lock->>Mem: zeroize and discard
    Lock->>Ev: state_changed(locked, epoch 8)
    deactivate Lock
    Cmd->>Lock: commit_if_current(epoch 7)
    Lock-->>Cmd: denied(stale_authorization)
    Win->>Pump: resume
    Pump->>Lock: lock(resume)
    Lock->>Ev: duplicate_lock(no secret fields)
